  Locus:
    Page: 88
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Death
---
We only die once and the great mystery is in knowing what it is going to be
like. How can we possibly prepare for it? The answer is that death exists
within life. Life is just a series of changes. All the little deaths that
occur within life are teaching us to let go.
